(1383, 119, 'our_live_text', 'Congratulations! The 3rd-year student of the specialty \"Information systems\" Asetuly Sherkhan took the 2nd place in the Republican competition of Scientific research works of students of higher educational institutions of the Republic of Kazakhstan. The topic of the scientific work is \"Modeling the melody of the anthem of the Republic of Kazakhstan on Arduino\". The head of the scientific project is Candidate of Physical and Mathematical Sciences, Associate professor, Аcademician MAIN Rystygulova Venera Botabaevna. The melody of the anthem of the Republic of Kazakhstan was first performed on the Arduino platform. An author\'s certificate has been received for the program code from Kazpatent. The use of Arduino to play the national anthem opens up new perspectives in the field of music technology and highlights the importance of innovation in the preservation and promotion of cultural heritage.'),
