(2430, 206, 'news_text', 'On November 28-30, 2024, the forum \"IV School of Rectors \"New Universities in the era of AI was held.:HR vs AI\", which was attended by the Minister of Science and Higher Education of the Republic of Kazakhstan Nurbek Sayasat, members of the government and the Rector and Vice-rector of universities of the Republic of Kazakhstan, as well as representatives of universities and foreign guests and practitioners. Among the invited guests is Ph.D. in Economics, Associate Professor Alpysbaeva Ainur Kunanbaevna of the Department of Finance and Accounting at KAZUTB named after K. Kulazhanov.  Minister of Science and Higher Education of the Republic of Kazakhstan Nurbek Sayasat made a report on the state and development of science and education, as well as highlighted the opening of new universities with the participation of foreign partners, artificial intelligence and other interesting issues. Members of the Government, university rectors and public figures of the Republic of Kazakhstan presented their cases at the plenary sessions. Among the rectors who spoke, I would like to mention an excellent, informative case study by Askar Myrzakhmetovich Nametov, rector of the West Kazakhstan Agrarian and Technical University named after Zhangir Khan Nametov.'),
